  "summary": "Malicious code in nic-datagov (npm)",
  "details": "This package contains a preinstall hook that runs on npm install. It collects the installer's hostname, username, and current working directory via hostname \u0026\u0026 whoami \u0026\u0026 pwd, then sends the data to webhook[.]site/1ea0386f-dcc0-4f1b-bdbb-61732d6535fb/nic-datagov over HTTP POST. webhook[.]site is a request-capture service commonly abused for data exfiltration. The package contains no functional code beyond this recon payload.",
